WEBVTT

00:00:28.125 --> 00:00:30.875
driving 500 miles to Shanghai Airport.

00:00:31.833 --> 00:00:35.250
The entire time, she was terrified
the authorities would arrest her.

00:00:36.458 --> 00:00:38.500
She made it out
on one of the last flights.

00:00:40.542 --> 00:00:42.809
So we're all relieved
that she's back home,

00:00:42.833 --> 00:00:44.625
safe in the US.

00:00:45.667 --> 00:00:48.625
But what if I told you
she was in this room?

00:00:50.042 --> 00:00:52.292
What if I told you
she was sitting next to you?

00:00:54.500 --> 00:00:56.434
There's no vaccine.

00:00:56.458 --> 00:01:00.601
There won't be a vaccine
for at least 12 months.